<br>
On the note of camping RF: When my turn comes, I plan on having a char in the lair as close to 100% of the time as I can. I will try to take a couple of days off work, and I will do everything I can to make getting in touch with me, online or off, as easy as possible. Some of my guild-mates will have my phone number, I will list all of the possible alts I might be on in this thread, and will do everything I can to make it easy to contact me, if he happens to pop when I am not online. I would suggest each cleric do as much as they can to make sure that they are informed as soon as RF pops. If someone other than my guild even finds out RF is up before I do, then I will be shocked.  <p><h6><a href="mailto:cuchulaine_eq@hotmail.com">Geneze Angelfyre</a><br>
