<br>
This mostly came about through a desire to see more structure and a process for camp-failures. We can either go with the new rules I've posted, or we can remove them, and keep going with what we've always had, with the list-holder pretty much deciding how issues need to be handled as they come up. <br>
<br>
One thing to think about though, if you want a process to actually be able to remove clerics for camp-failures, you'd better be willing to live under that same process yourself. <p>Cayleu Starshine
